arianelli, who won the Academy Award…. [But now] I am very excited to do something more with a more modern beat.\r\n\r\nAccording to Wright, the general public will see a trailer “soon.”', 'Hanna Preview and Panel – Saturday October 9, 12:30 PM', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '106-revision-6', '', '', '2010-10-12 18:01:00', '2010-10-12 18:01:00', '', 106, 'http://recess.nujigroup.com/?p=116', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
