 he really needs to take on roles of a more consistent body weight.\r\n\r\n8:04 - Ricky Gervais is already offending people, targeting perhaps the two worst nominations of the year, <em>Burlesque</em> and<em> The Tourist</em>.  He also makes fun of Scientologists and gets a big "ooooh" from the audience.  Get over yourselves.', 'The 68th Annual Golden Globe Awards - Live Blog', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '462-revision-21', '', '', '2011-01-17 02:07:26', '2011-01-17 02:07:26', '', 462, 'http://recess.nujigroup.com/?p=493', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
