joke than a serious endeavor. This might work better as a tour DVD with commentary and documentary footage. As it stands, <em>The Fall</em> can’t escape the sentiment of, “Dude, you had to be there.”', 'Gorillaz: The Fall Review', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '701-revision-2', '', '', '2011-04-21 21:38:50', '2011-04-21 21:38:50', '', 701, 'http://recess.nujigroup.com/?p=703', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
